### Expected behavior

Hover of embedded graphs are disappearing in full screen mode since the version 3.3 of bokeh.
I tested 3.1.1 ==> works fine 
            3.2.2 ==> works fine 
            3.3.4 and above ==> hover disappearing in full screen mode


### Observed behavior

The hover is not visible when the plot is in fullscreen

